{"tid":158943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲明早到庭聲援 「請自行帶備帽雨傘外套口罩」","createTime":"2017-03-16T15:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T08:04:52.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6f1dfa07c9315209fd291b8bb28a8008b0dd7d","tid":158943,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489677447_ff77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489677447_ff77.jpg&h=b144e916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂案中兩男一女被告被裁定暴動罪成，還柙至明早判刑。有組織「香港民族陣綫」以【義士蒙難】為題於Facebook留帖文，稱「今日，魚蛋革命中被控暴動罪的三位義士被判罪名成立，並將於明日上午十一點三十分於灣仔區域法院十一樓三十六庭判刑，本組織呼籲各方同道，到場聲援義士。歷經漫長的審訊及逼害，魚革義士極需同道關注及支持」。<br />\n<br />\n該帖文又謂「計劃到場聲援的同道請自行帶備帽，雨傘，外套及口罩，以保障自身私隱」，並「謹祝義士一切平安」。本土民主前線亦轉發帖文。"},{"pid":"e9ad2b3222b7c01dae0483a3f8fbfc28358d8d97","tid":158943,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"277b0295844d9de56ca58a4c85c25829ef91341b","tid":158943,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fb82746c2a7e646e684bb4ef51af5540a0b5e2d","tid":158943,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"入到court咪又係要除<br />\n多餘"},{"pid":"d3285e23c6dff463b293c4b0a39eab159165dbf4","tid":158943,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6540493e299994a15e8da3d742eabcf22d360c36","tid":158943,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:40:23.000Z","msg":"左膠點柒都有班黃傘鳩嗚團<br />\n勇武本土撚得一兩個口罩人<br />\n大亨/天埼/偉哥/國c/毓炆/梁游/堡主去咗邊"},{"pid":"5a3361fc8bae02051c28bd5f32073a9b843d467d","tid":158943,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,